<div style="font-size: inherit;"><h1 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Dashboard Management</h1><h3 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Dashboard Creation</h3><ul style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li>User can create a new dashboard with a name</li><li>User can add different types of widgets:<ul><li>Charts (line, bar, pie)</li><li>Number cards</li><li>Data tables</li><li>Text widgets</li><li><br></li></ul></li><li>User can set dashboard layout (grid-based)</li><li>Add data validation for the charts</li></ul><h3 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Dashboard Customization</h3><ul style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li>User can:<ul><li>Drag and drop widgets to rearrange</li><li>Resize widgets</li><li>Edit widget titles and data sources</li><li>Set refresh intervals</li></ul></li><li>Changes auto-save while editing</li></ul><h3 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Dashboard Management</h3><ul style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li>User can view list of all dashboards</li><li>User can duplicate existing dashboards</li><li>User can delete dashboards with confirmation</li><li>User can share dashboard view link</li></ul><h2 style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Definition of Done</h2><ul style="text-align: start; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><li>Dashboards save and load correctly</li><li>Widgets display accurate data</li><li>Layout changes persist after refresh</li><li>Sharing links work correctly</li></ul><br></div>
